  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Intravenous iron</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Women will receive iron sucrose (sacrofer ampules 100 mg/5ml) A patient's total body iron deficit will be calculated using the Ganzoni formula (total iron dose = [body weight (kilogram)× (15-actual Hemoglobin)] × 2.4 + 500 mg) then the total dose will be divided on 3 settings</description>
  </arm_group>
